02:07:09,380 --> 02:07:11,780
我只想和你谈谈。等等..。
I just want to talk to you. Wait...

1488
02:07:29,540 --> 02:07:32,260
你不能上唐纳森的课。那真是令人厌烦。
You're not taking Donaldson's class. That's a real bore.

1489
02:07:32,340 --> 02:07:34,020
我该带些什么呢？
What shall I take?

1490
02:07:34,660 --> 02:07:36,140
我没有把握。
I'm not sure.

1491
02:07:36,700 --> 02:07:39,500
见鬼的“全球发展研究”是什么？
What the hell is "Global Development Studies"?

1492
02:07:40,220 --> 02:07:43,020
我得旁听那件事，然后告诉你。
I'll have to sit in on that one and let you know.

1493
02:07:44,260 --> 02:07:47,260
