'Bye, Mom. 'Bye, Dad.

1501
02:08:08,380 --> 02:08:10,140
那是个保姆吗？
That's a babysitter?

1502
02:08:35,740 --> 02:08:37,940
我以为我们要去看电影。
I thought we were going to the movies.

1503
02:08:42,180 --> 02:08:43,900
我们去什么地方？
Where are we going?

1504
02:08:53,660 --> 02:08:54,820
我明白了。
I see.

1505
02:08:55,860 --> 02:08:58,500
我们要留在这里看孩子们。
We're going to stay here and look at the kids.

1506
02:08:59,860 --> 02:09:01,100
这真是个不错的约会。
This is some date.

1507
02:09:06,980 --> 02:09:08,540
你怀念写作吗？
Do you miss writing?

1508
02:09:08,780 --> 02:09:11,580
不用谢。如果我这么做了，我会重新开始的。
Not at all. If I do, I'll start again.

1509
02:09:12,700 --> 02:09:16,340
不过你知道我真正喜欢的是什么吗？想着所有的事情。
You know what I really love, though? Thinking about everything.

1510
02:09:17,260 --> 02:09:18,140
我们是怎么认识的。
How we met.

1511
02:09:18,860 --> 02:09:20,140
所有这些。
All that.

1512
02:09:20,860 --> 02:09:23,180
-你不能活在过去。-我没有
- You can't live in the past. - I'm not.

1513
02:09:23,660 --> 02:09:26,300
但我可以活在现在，回想过去。
But I can live in the present, and think about the past.

1514
02:09:26,380 --> 02:09:28,900
你应该在年纪大、头发花白的时候才这么做。
You're supposed to do that when you're old and gray.

1515
02:09:28,980 --> 02:09:30,340
让它见鬼去吧。
To hell with that.

1516
02:09:30,380 --> 02:09:33,580
当我又老又白的时候，我可能不会记得我的过去了。
When I'm old and gray, I probably won't remember my past.

1517
02:09:33,740 --> 02:09:35,500
你做这件事的时候一定要年轻。
You've got to be young when you do it.

1518
02:09:36,980 --> 02:09:40,780
真的很不错，你知道吗？回首往事，看到你生命的弧线。
It's really nice, you know? To look back and see the arc of your life.

1519
02:09:40,860 --> 02:09:42,580
这一切都是有联系的。
It's all connected.

1520
02:09:42,820 --> 02:09:45,020
你是怎么从那里到这里的..。
How you got from there to here...

1521
02:09:45,860 --> 02:09:47,900
去看看队伍，你知道吗？
To see the line, you know?

1522
02:09:50,060 --> 02:09:52,100
这真的是一次冒险。
It really has been an adventure.

1523
02:09:52,780 --> 02:09:54,740
我又要开始教书了。
I'm going to start teaching again.

1524
02:09:54,860 --> 02:09:57,020
我要开始玩悬挂式滑翔了。
I'm going to take up hang-gliding.

1525
02:10:07,060 --> 02:10:09,940
这就是你一直想要的。
This is what you had in mind all along.

1526
02:10:12,700 --> 02:10:16,380
我打赌我知道我们以后能做什么。
And I bet I know what we can do later on.

1527
02:10:17,900 --> 02:10:20,900
孩子们睡着了，我们去看看。
We'll go look at the kids when they're asleep.

1528
02:10:23,260 --> 02:10:24,620
海伦·霍姆。
Helen Holm.

1529
02:10:36,540 --> 02:10:37,500
去!
Go!

1530
02:10:41,020 --> 02:10:42,740
去吧，马丁。赶快!
Go, Martin. Come on!

1531
02:10:43,260 --> 02:10:44,780
把他拿下！
Take him down!

1532
02:10:46,580 --> 02:10:48,540
就这样。走得好！
That's it. Good move!

1533
02:10:48,620 --> 02:10:49,740
