Ten seconds!

1534
02:10:50,900 --> 02:10:52,580
来吧，马丁。骑他！
Come on, Martin. Ride him!

1535
02:10:55,260 --> 02:10:56,780
来吧，埃尔默。
Come on, Elmer.

1536
02:10:58,060 --> 02:10:59,860
