Get off your back, Virgil.

1538
02:11:06,100 --> 02:11:08,500
把他绑在下面。就这样。
Tie him up underneath. That's it.

1539
02:11:08,820 --> 02:11:10,220
十秒！
Ten seconds!

1540
02:11:12,340 --> 02:11:13,740
在他后面，马库斯！
Behind him, Marcus!

1541
