Behind him. Bring him down!

1543
02:11:20,780 --> 02:11:21,740
噗！
Pooh!

1544
02:11:34,940 --> 02:11:39,300
快找人来！快点！快叫医生来！
Get someone! Quickly! Get a doctor!

1545
02:11:39,340 --> 02:11:40,980
快叫救护车！
Get an ambulance!

1546
02:11:42,140 --> 02:11:44,100
哦，天哪，拜托！
Oh, God, please!

1547
02:12:28,820 --> 02:12:31,020
我们要带你去波士顿的一家医院。
We're taking you to a hospital in Boston.

1548
02:12:31,420 --> 02:12:33,420
一切都会顺利的。
Everything will be fine.

1549
02:12:34,980 --> 02:12:36,140
海伦？
Helen?

1550
02:12:42,420 --> 02:12:43,660
记住。
Remember.

1551
02:12:44,380 --> 02:12:45,860
什么，亲爱的？
What, my love?

1552
02:12:47,220 --> 02:12:48,900
一切，海伦。
Everything, Helen.

1553
02:12:50,620 --> 02:12:52,100
是的，亲爱的。
Yes, my love.

1554
02:12:58,060 --> 02:12:59,740
我在飞，海伦。
I'm flying, Helen.

1555
02:13:04,580 --> 02:13:05,900
是的，亲爱的。
Yes, my love.

1556
02:13:08,700 --> 02:13:10,460
我在飞。
I'm flying.

1557
